@startuml ffmpeg_sequence
scale 2
title "UML Sequence Diagram - FFmpeg GUI Conversion"

actor User

User -> FfmpegGUI: Select input file

User -> FfmpegGUI: Choose output format
User -> FfmpegGUI: Click Convert


FfmpegGUI -> Converter: run ffmpeg command

Converter -> ConversionLog: add entry
ConversionLog -> Converter: log stored

Converter -> FfmpegGUI: conversion status returned

FfmpegGUI -> User: show success/failure message

User -> FfmpegGUI: View Conversion Log
FfmpegGUI -> ConversionLog: ask to show window
ConversionLog -> User: display log window

@enduml